        }
        ul__searchTextBox1 += "</ul>";

            // UnHighlight all other elements before highlighting selected element
            $("#resultDiv1 .HighLightMe").removeClass("pretty-hover");

                    if (charCode == 38)//up arrow

                        if ($('#resultDiv1 .pretty-hover').length > 0) { //an element is highlighted
                            $('#resultDiv1 li.HighLightMe').each(function () {
